# 运行时与构建产物（勿提交 vendor / 绿色版 dist 目录）
weibo-collector/vendor/
weibo-collector/dist/CSLSentinel/
weibo-collector/build/
# 安装包/压缩包体积 >100MB，不要进普通 git（见 README：用 GitHub Releases 或网盘）
weibo-collector/dist.zip
weibo-collector/dist/*.exe
weibo-collector/.env
weibo-collector/data/*
!weibo-collector/data/.gitkeep
weibo-collector/reports/*
!weibo-collector/reports/.gitkeep
weibo-collector/logs/*
!weibo-collector/logs/.gitkeep

__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
*.pyc

